        <p class="lead-text">A MOHRE work permit rejection delays your start date, costs your employer money, and adds weeks to the visa timeline. Most rejections trace back to document problems that could have been caught early. This guide covers the specific issues we see repeatedly and how to prevent them.</p>

        <div class="callout-block">
